article.headline: Saint Joseph's (PA) secures 70-63 victory against Navy
article.description: — Erik Reynolds II's 29 points helped Saint Joseph's (PA) defeat Navy 70-63 on Monday night.
article.linkText: Saint Joseph's (PA) secures 70-63 victory against Navy
article.story: PHILADELPHIA -- — Erik Reynolds II's 29 points helped Saint Joseph's (PA) defeat Navy 70-63 on Monday night. Reynolds also contributed five rebounds for the Hawks. Xzayvier Brown added 22 points while shooting 5 for 11 (1 for 4 from 3-point range) and 11 of 12 from the free-throw line. Austin Benigni led the Midshipmen in scoring, finishing with 23 points and three steals. Navy also got 12 points, nine rebounds and two steals from Aidan Kehoe. Jordan Pennick also had 11 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
